This kind of highlighting/coloring has no effect when a rule is injecting new code (missing in the original code), like rule #4 (inject missing stdgates include).
This whole highlighting/coloring + tooltips does not depend on the activation state of the rules: the activation state of the rules controls how the rewriting happens in the Rewritten code, not how the Original code gets highlighted/colored.
